\v 3 Njalo loba nini ekufikeni kwami, loba ngobani\x + 2 Kor. 8.18,19.\x* elibakhethileyo, ngezincwadi\x + Roma 2.18.\x*, laba ngizabathuma ukuze base isipho senu somusa eJerusalema;
\v 4 njalo uba kufanele ukuthi lami ngihambe, bazahamba lami.
