\v 7 Ngoba kangifisi ukulibona khathesinje ekwedluleni\x + 2 Kor. 1.15,16.\x*; kodwa ngithemba ukuhlala lani isikhathi esithile, uba iNkosi ivuma\x + Seb. 18.21.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa ngizahlala eEfesu\x + Seb. 18.19.\x* kuze kufike \w iPentekoste\w**\x + Seb. 20.16.\x*;
