\v 10 Nxa-ke\x + 4.17. 2 Kor. 1.1.\x* uTimothi\x + Seb. 16.1.\x* engafika, bonani ukuthi ulani engelakwesaba; ngoba usebenza\x + Roma 16.21. 1 Thes. 3.2. Fil. 2.20,22.\x* umsebenzi weNkosi\x + 15.58.\x* njengami futhi.
\v 11 Ngakho kakungabi khona omdelelayo\x + 1 Tim. 4.12.\x*; kodwa mdluliseni\x + Seb. 15.3.\x* ngokuthula\x + Seb. 15.33.\x*, ukuze eze kimi; ngoba ngimlindele kanye labazalwane.
\v 12 Njalo mayelana lomzalwane uApolosi\x + 1.12; 3.5. Seb. 18.24.\x*, ngamkhuthaza kakhulu ukuze eze kini kanye labazalwane; kodwa kwakungeyisiyo intando \add yakhe\add* lakanye ukuthi eze khathesi, kodwa uzakuza nxa eselethuba.
